WEBVTT

00:04:01.667 --> 00:04:03.476
But not him.

00:04:03.500 --> 00:04:07.184
He approached me with empathy

00:04:07.208 --> 00:04:09.042
and with flexibility.

00:04:09.917 --> 00:04:12.768
I was so grateful for that.

00:04:12.792 --> 00:04:17.684
He saw this six-year-old
was tired and weary.

00:04:17.708 --> 00:04:20.559
And so instead of making me
go outside for recess,

00:04:20.583 --> 00:04:22.851
he would let me stay in and take naps,

00:04:22.875 --> 00:04:25.667
because he knew I needed rest.

00:04:27.208 --> 00:04:30.851
Instead of sitting
at the teacher table at lunch,